@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001
@username = admin
@password = password

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Login — Obtains a JWT access token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{username}}&password={{password}}

### Store the access token from the login response
@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Verify token validity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inspect current token scopes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/my-scopes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hash a plain-text password (no auth required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/hash-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "password": "new-password"
}
